items.sentence: In order to make a phone call, I put my hand in my pocket and searched for a coin.
I saw a red car and a white one. The red one was nicer looking than the white one.
My life would probably have been quite different if I had been born a month later.
Even if you fail the first time you try it, don't give up, but try doing it again.
Little did I know Tom and Mary were playing footsy under the table the whole time.
